thread.title: BRIEF-Phillips 66 Partners To Construct West Texas Crude Oil Pipeline System

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Phillips 66 Partners To Construct West Texas Crude Oil Pipeline System

organizations.name: partners to construct west texas crude oil pipeline system

text:
Phillips 66 Partners LP:
* PHILLIPS 66 PARTNERS TO CONSTRUCT WEST TEXAS CRUDE OIL PIPELINE SYSTEM, HOLD SECOND OPEN SEASON
* PHILLIPS 66 PARTNERS LP - PIPELINE IS EXPECTED TO BE PLACED IN SERVICE BY END OF 2019
* PHILLIPS 66 PARTNERS - RECEIVED SUFFICIENT BINDING COMMITMENTS ON AN INITIAL OPEN SEASON TO PROCEED WITH CONSTRUCTION OF GRAY OAK PIPELINE SYSTEM
* PHILLIPS 66 PARTNERS LP - GRAY OAK PIPELINE SECOND OPEN SEASON WILL COMMENCE AT 3 P.M. CDT ON APRIL 26, 2018
* PHILLIPS 66 PARTNERS LP - GRAY OAK PIPELINE, A JV OWNED 75 PERCENT BY CO AND 25 PERCENT BY ANDEAVOR WILL OWN PIPELINE SYSTEM Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Reuters.Briefs@thomsonreuters.com)
